  "decision_conditions": [
    "Condition : 1 - The development shall be carried out in accordance with the reports, specifications and drawings detailed 596801-2, 596801-3, 596801-4, Location Plan by Buy A Plan. \r\nReason: To ensure a satisfactory standard of development and to allow the local planning authority to review any potential changes to the scheme. \r\n",
    "Condition : 2 - The maximum steady brightness of the fascia and roundel signs hereby permitted is not to exceed 500 candelas per sq.m.\r\nReason: To ensure the sign does not have an adverse effect on the amenity of the area in accordance with Council policy LP9 and to comply with paragraph 132 of the National Planning Policy Framework 2023.\r\n",
    "Condition : 3 - The maximum steady brightness of the projecting signs hereby permitted is not to exceed 200 candelas per sq.m. \r\nReason: To ensure the proposed sign does not have an adverse effect on the amenity of the area in accordance with Council policy LP9 of the Wandsworth Local Plan (adopted July 2023) and to comply with paragraph 132 of the National Planning Policy Framework 2023.\r\n",
    "Condition : 4 - The illumination of the signs hereby permitted shall be by static illumination only. \r\nReason: In the interest of highway safety and of the visual amenities of the locality in accordance with Council policy LP9 and to comply with paragraph 132 of the National Planning Policy Framework 2023.\r\n"
